ISLAMABAD, Feb 20 (APP):Prime Minister Imran Khan chaired a meeting regarding the Pakistan Steel Mills here on Thursday.
The meeting was attended by Minister for Maritime Affairs Syed Ali Haider Zaidi, Minister for Planning Asad Umar, Minister for Privatization Muhammad Mian Soomro, Advisor on Finance Dr Abdul Hafeez Sheikh, Advisor on Commerce Abdul Razaq Dawood, Advisor on Institutional Reforms Dr Ishrat Hussain, Special Assistant to the PM Nadeem Babar and senior officers.
